vernac_cmds: Lemma derivable_eq : forall (context context' : flist) (a a' : form), context = context' -> a = a' -> Derivable context a -> Derivable context' a'.
intros context context' a a' eq_context eq_a.
Lemma derivable_subst : forall (i : Int) (g : form) (context : flist) (a : form), Derivable context a -> Derivable (subst_list i g context) (subst_form i g a).
intros i g context a der.
elim der; clear der a t context.
intros context t a der ih.
apply Derivable_Intro with (Efq t1 (subst_form i g a)).
intros context a t b der ih.
apply Derivable_Intro with (Abs (subst_form i g a) t1).
intros context r s a b der_r ih_r der_s ih_s.
apply Derivable_Intro with (App (subst_form i g a) r1 s1).
intros context r s a b der_r ih_r der_s ih_s.
intros context r a b der_r ih.
elim ih; clear ih; intros r1 der_r1.
apply Derivable_Intro with (PrL (subst_form i g b) r1).
intros context r a b der_r ih.
elim ih; clear ih; intros r1 der_r1.
apply Derivable_Intro with (PrR (subst_form i g a) r1).
intros context r a b der_r ih.
elim ih; clear ih; intros r1 der_r1.
apply Derivable_Intro with (OrFL r1 (subst_form i g b)).
intros context r a b der_r ih.
elim ih; clear ih; intros r1 der_r1.
apply Derivable_Intro with (OrFR r1 (subst_form i g a)).
intros context r s t a b c der_r ih_r der_s ih_s der_t ih_t.
elim ih_r; clear ih_r; intros r1 der_r1.
elim ih_s; clear ih_s; intros s1 der_s1.
elim ih_t; clear ih_t; intros t1 der_t1.
apply Derivable_Intro with (Cas (subst_form i g a) (subst_form i g b) r1 s1 t1).
intros context r a b der_r ih_r.
elim ih_r; clear ih_r; intros r1 der_r1.
Lemma snd_order_inst : forall (context : flist) (i : Int), Derivable context (Atom i) -> below_list context i -> forall b : form, Derivable context b.
intros context i der below b.
Lemma derivable_weak : forall (context : flist) (a b : form), Derivable context a -> Derivable (b :: context) a.
Lemma derivable_weak_list : forall (context1 context2 : flist) (a : form), Derivable context1 a -> Derivable (context2 ++ context1) a.

Lemma derivable_cut_aux : forall (context : flist) (t : proof_term) (b : form), derives context t b -> forall (a : form) (l1 l2 : flist), context = l1 ++ a :: l2 -> Derivable fnil a -> Derivable (l1 ++ l2) b.
elim der_t; clear der_t context t b.
intros context n a nth b l1 l2 eq_context.
elim (inv_nth_app form n l1 (b :: l2) a nth); clear nth.
clear n; intros n; case n; clear n.
rewrite (inv_nthO form b l2 a nth_eq).
intros context t a der_t ih b l1 l2 eq_context der_b.
elim (ih b l1 l2); try assumption.
intros context a t b der_t ih c l1 l2 eq_context der_c.
elim (ih c (a :: l1) l2); clear ih.
intros context r s a b der_r ih_r der_s ih_s c l1 l2 eq_context der_c.
elim (ih_r c l1 l2); clear ih_r; try assumption.
elim (ih_s c l1 l2); clear ih_s; try assumption.
apply Derivable_Intro with (App a r0 s0).
intros context r s a b der_r ih_r der_s ih_s c l1 l2 eq_context der_c.
elim (ih_r c l1 l2); clear ih_r; try assumption.
elim (ih_s c l1 l2); clear ih_s; try assumption.
intros context r a b der_r ih_r c l1 l2 eq_context der_c.
elim (ih_r c l1 l2); clear ih_r; try assumption.
intros context r a b der_r ih_r c l1 l2 eq_context der_c.
elim (ih_r c l1 l2); clear ih_r; try assumption.
intros context r a b der_r ih_r c l1 l2 eq_context der_c.
elim (ih_r c l1 l2); clear ih_r; try assumption.
intros context r a b der_r ih_r c l1 l2 eq_context der_c.
elim (ih_r c l1 l2); clear ih_r; try assumption.
intros context r s t a b c der_r ih_r der_s ih_s der_t ih_t d l1 l2 eq_context der_d; clear der_r der_s der_t.
elim (ih_r d l1 l2); try assumption; clear ih_r.
elim (ih_s d (a :: l1) l2); clear ih_s.
elim (ih_t d (b :: l1) l2); clear ih_t.
apply Derivable_Intro with (Cas a b r0 s0 t0).
intros context r a b der_r ih_r c l1.
simpl in |- *; intros l2 eq_context der_c.
simpl in |- *; intros d l1 l2 eq_context der_c.
elim (ih_r c l1 l2); clear ih_r; try assumption.
Lemma derivable_cut : forall (context : flist) (a b : form), Derivable fnil a -> Derivable (a :: context) b -> Derivable context b.
intros context a b der_a der_b.
apply (derivable_cut_aux (a :: context) t b der_b a fnil context).
Lemma derivable_cut_merge : forall (context : flist) (a b : form), Derivable context a -> Derivable (a :: context) b -> Derivable context b.
intros context; elim context; clear context.
intros; apply derivable_cut with a; assumption.
intros c context ih a b der_a der_b.
elim (ih (Imp c a) (Imp c b)); clear ih.
elim der_a; clear der_a; intros t der_t.
elim der_b; clear der_b; intros t der_t.
apply Derivable_Intro with (Abs c (App a (App c (Shift (Shift (Abs c (Abs a t)))) (Var 0)) (App c (Var 1) (Var 0)))).
Lemma derivable_a_imp_a : forall a : form, Derivable fnil (Imp a a).
Lemma derivable_a_and_b__derivable_a : forall (a b : form) (context : flist), Derivable context (AndF a b) -> Derivable context a.
Lemma derivable_a_and_b__derivable_b : forall (a b : form) (context : flist), Derivable context (AndF a b) -> Derivable context b.
Lemma derivable_falsum_or_a__derivable_a : forall (a : form) (context : flist), Derivable context (OrF Falsum a) -> Derivable context a.
apply Derivable_Intro with (Cas Falsum a t (Efq (Var 0) a) (Var 0)).
Lemma derivable_a_or_falsum__derivable_a : forall (a : form) (context : flist), Derivable context (OrF a Falsum) -> Derivable context a.
apply Derivable_Intro with (Cas a Falsum t (Var 0) (Efq (Var 0) a)).
Lemma derivable_a_imp_falsum_or_b__derivable_a_imp_b : forall (context : flist) (a b : form), Derivable context (Imp a (OrF Falsum b)) -> Derivable context (Imp a b).
apply Derivable_Intro with (Abs a (Cas Falsum b (App a (Shift t) (Var 0)) (Efq (Var 0) b) (Var 0))).
Lemma derivable_a_imp_b_or_falsum__derivable_a_imp_b : forall (context : flist) (a b : form), Derivable context (Imp a (OrF b Falsum)) -> Derivable context (Imp a b).
apply Derivable_Intro with (Abs a (Cas b Falsum (App a (Shift t) (Var 0)) (Var 0) (Efq (Var 0) b))).
Lemma derivable_a0_and_a1_imp_b__derivable_a0_imp_a1_imp_b : forall (a0 a1 b : form) (context : flist), Derivable context (Imp (AndF a0 a1) b) -> Derivable context (Imp a0 (Imp a1 b)).
intros a0 a1 b context der.
apply Derivable_Intro with (Abs a0 (Abs a1 (App (AndF a0 a1) (Shift (Shift t)) (Pair (Var 1) (Var 0))))).
Lemma derivable_a0_or_a1_imp_b__derivable_a0_imp_b : forall (context : flist) (a0 a1 b : form), Derivable context (Imp (OrF a0 a1) b) -> Derivable context (Imp a0 b).
intros context a0 a1 b der.
apply Derivable_Intro with (Abs a0 (App (OrF a0 a1) (Shift t) (OrFL (Var 0) a1))).
Lemma derivable_a0_or_a1_imp_b__derivable_a1_imp_b : forall (context : flist) (a0 a1 b : form), Derivable context (Imp (OrF a0 a1) b) -> Derivable context (Imp a1 b).
intros context a0 a1 b der.
apply Derivable_Intro with (Abs a1 (App (OrF a0 a1) (Shift t) (OrFR (Var 0) a0))).
Lemma derivable_falsum_imp_b_imp_c__derivable_c : forall (context : flist) (b c : form), Derivable context (Imp (Imp Falsum b) c) -> Derivable context c.
apply Derivable_Intro with (App (Imp Falsum b) t (Abs Falsum (Efq (Var 0) b))).
Lemma derivable_b__derivable_a_imp_b : forall (a b : form) (context : flist), Derivable context b -> Derivable context (Imp a b).
Lemma derivable_a_a_imp_b__derivable_b : forall (a b : form) (context : flist), Derivable context a -> Derivable context (Imp a b) -> Derivable context b.
intros a b context der_a der_ab.
apply Derivable_Intro with (App a s t).
Lemma derivable_a_context_b__derivable_a_imp_b : forall (a b : form) (context : flist), Derivable (a :: context) b -> Derivable context (Imp a b).

Lemma derivable_vimp : forall (context : flist) (l : list Int) (a b : form), (forall context : flist, Derivable context a -> Derivable context b) -> Derivable context (vimp l a) -> Derivable context (vimp l b).
simpl in |- *; intros i l ih a b der_ab der_a.
apply ih with (a := Imp (Atom i) a); try assumption.
elim der_ia; clear der_ia; intros t der_ia.

Lemma derivable_vimp2 : forall (context : flist) (l : list Int) (a b c : form), (forall context : flist, Derivable context a -> Derivable context b -> Derivable context c) -> Derivable context (vimp l a) -> Derivable context (vimp l b) -> Derivable context (vimp l c).
intros a b c der_abc der_a der_b.
simpl in |- *; intros i l ih a b c der_abc der_a der_b.
apply ih with (a := Imp (Atom i) a) (b := Imp (Atom i) b); try assumption.
elim der_ia; clear der_ia; intros t der_ia.
elim der_ib; clear der_ib; intros s der_ib.
Lemma derivable_vimp0 : forall (context : flist) (l : list Int) (a : form), (forall context : flist, Derivable context a) -> Derivable context (vimp l a).
simpl in |- *; intros i l ih a der_a.
elim der_a with (Atom i :: context'); clear der_a; intros t der_a.
